  "updated": 1752317390,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6872345ea76c6d201b696aa1",
      "text": "Dockerの中でClaudeCodeを使う方法のメモ書き",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1752314975,
      "updated": 1752314975
    },
    {
      "id": "6872345f00000000007976a6",
      "text": "from [2025/07/12]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1752314975,
      "updated": 1752314975
    },
    {
      "id": "68723a4500000000007cd649",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1752316485,
      "updated": 1752316485
    },
    {
      "id": "6872345f00000000007976a7",
      "text": "[Docker]の中で[Claude Code]を使う方法のメモ書き[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1752314975,
      "updated": 1752315011
    },
    {
      "id": "6872345f00000000007976a8",
      "text": " ClaudeCodeをフリーダムに使うため(--dangerously-skip-permissions)のDocker環境構築",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1752314975,
      "updated": 1752314994
    },
    {
      "id": "6872345f00000000007976a9",
      "text": " →Anthropic公式のリポジトリがいい感じに設定されてる",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1752314975,
      "updated": 1752314997
    },
    {
      "id": "6872345f00000000007976aa",
      "text": " \thttps://github.com/anthropics/claude-code/",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1752314975,
      "updated": 1752314997
    },
    {
      "id": "6872345f00000000007976ab",
      "text": " \t.devcontainer/の設定で、いい感じに蓋されたDocker環境が用意できる",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1752314975,
      "updated": 1752317346
    },
    {
      "id": "68723a7f00000000007cd64c",
      "text": " \t\tこぴって自分用のミニマム環境を作った https://github.com/taktamur/copy-claude-code",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1752316543,
      "updated": 1752316595
    },
    {
      "id": "68723d790000000000ffc87e",
      "text": " \t\t.devcontainer/は、[Development Containers]の設定置き場らしい？",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1752317306,
      "updated": 1752317354
    },
    {
      "id": "6872345f00000000007976ac",
      "text": " \t[VSCode]の拡張機能のdevContainerを使うと、VSCodeで開いた時に、Dockerで起動するのをお勧めされる",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1752314975,
      "updated": 1752317364
    },
    {
      "id": "6872345f00000000007976ad",
      "text": " \tVSCodeの中のターミナルで`claude --dangerously-skip-permissions`",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1752314975,
      "updated": 1752314997
    },
    {
      "id": "6872345f00000000007976ae",
      "text": " \t\t→ ClaudeCodeが反乱を起こしてrm ~/ しても、Dockerだから被害が出なくなる。",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1752314975,
      "updated": 1752314997
    },
    {
      "id": "6872345f00000000007976af",
      "text": " ホスト側とコンテナ側で、ClaudeCodeの認証を共通化しようとすると多分ダメっぽい",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1752314975,
      "updated": 1752314997
    },
    {
      "id": "6872345f00000000007976b0",
      "text": " \tホストがMac、コンテナがLinuxと違ってて、認証情報の保存方法が違うらしい。",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1752314975,
      "updated": 1752314997
    },
    {
      "id": "687239420000000000c08393",
      "text": " githubの認証情報も、当然ながら共有されてない",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1752316227,
      "updated": 1752316237
    },
    {
      "id": "6872394d0000000000c08394",
      "text": " \tgitのコミットはできる。",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1752316237,
      "updated": 1752317390
    },
    {
      "id": "68723dc90000000000ffc87f",
      "text": " \tコンテナ側でいちいち認証するのも面倒だから、githubへのpushはホスト側でやった方が良さそう",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1752317385,
      "updated": 1752317385
    },
